en.purpose: To represent data points recorded during a simple pelvic ultrasound scan, including description and simple measures of uterus, ovaries, adnexal mass and the rectouterine pouch.
en.use:
Use for representing a simple pelvic ultrasound scan in non-pregnant individuals.

The element 'Modality' may be linked to DICOM CID 29 Acquisition Modality value set or other appropriate value set.
en.misuse: Not to be used during pelvic ultrasound scan in pregnancy. Use the 'Pelvic ultrasound, early pregnancy' or other appropriate template.
